<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Visual TV OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #001f3f; /* Dark navy blue */
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #1d1e1f; /* Slightly lighter navy blue */
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(75, 75, 75, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .otp {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2d2c2a; /* Highlight color */
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #cccccc;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>IntelliVibe AI API OTP Verification</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for signing up for IntelliVibe AI Please use the following OTP to verify your email address:</p>
            <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
            <p>This OTP is valid for 2 minutes.</p>
          
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you did not request this email, please ignore it.</p>
            <p>Â© <%= year %> IntelliVibe AI. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>